    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left to give its next owner! Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty handles the road like a champ. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. I'm super easy to talk to, so please feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus. This wide-body chassis retains its factory-correct AWD system and a precise 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. The M96 powerplant delivers linear torque through the rev range, while the C4S-specific suspension geometry and Turbo-derived 'Big Red' monoblock calipers ensure exceptional lateral grip and deceleration. Recent service includes a borescope inspection and an upgraded IMS bearing for peace of mind. Mechanically sound with crisp shift linkage and a responsive throttle map, this 911 is an ideal driver-spec example for the purist.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
      "price": 29500.0,
