    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver, maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity and interior preservation. The exterior finish presents beautifully, retaining a high gloss, though close inspection reveals minor road peppering on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with plush seating that shows only minimal softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly with a consistent idle, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. It has a complete service history, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. This car is ready for the road with no immediate maintenance required, offering a solid, rattle-free driving experience.",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both reliability and refinement. It exhibits a well-maintained exterior paired with a sophisticated, clean interior. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, the mechanical systems demonstrate consistent performance and structural soundness. This offering represents a superior balance of value and prestige, ideal for those seeking a dependable yet elevated driving experience.",
      "price": 31500.0,
