    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me and is still running great! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it. Perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
